# Project Structure Guide

## Core Components

The main components of the service learning management system are:

- **Codespaces Integration**: Located in [app/Services/CodespaceService.php](mdc:app/Services/CodespaceService.php)
- **Developer Credentials**: Managed through [app/Models/DeveloperCredential.php](mdc:app/Models/DeveloperCredential.php)
- **Configuration**: Main config in [config/codespaces.php](mdc:config/codespaces.php)
- **Documentation**: Generated using [app/Console/Commands/GenerateDocsCommand.php](mdc:app/Console/Commands/GenerateDocsCommand.php)

## Key Directories

- `.devcontainer/`: Contains Docker and Codespaces configuration
- `.github/workflows/`: GitHub Actions workflows for CI/CD
- `app/`: Core application code
- `docs/`: Generated documentation
- `tests/`: Test suites

## Important Files

- [README.md](mdc:README.md): Project overview and setup instructions
- [.env.example](mdc:.env.example): Environment configuration template
- [routes/codespaces.php](mdc:routes/codespaces.php): API routes for Codespaces
- [app/Providers/CodespaceServiceProvider.php](mdc:app/Providers/CodespaceServiceProvider.php): Service provider for Codespaces

## Testing Structure
Tests are organized in the `tests/` directory:

- `tests/Unit/` - Unit tests
  - [ServiceHealthAgentTest.php](mdc:tests/Unit/ServiceHealthAgentTest.php)
  - [DeploymentAutomationAgentTest.php](mdc:tests/Unit/DeploymentAutomationAgentTest.php)

- `tests/Integration/` - Integration tests
  - API endpoint tests
  - Database integration tests

## Configuration
Configuration files are stored in:

- `config/` - Application configuration
  - Environment-specific settings
  - Service configurations

## Documentation
Documentation is maintained in:

- `.reports/` - Test reports and documentation
  - [test_plan.md](mdc:.reports/test_plan.md) - Testing strategy
  - Implementation status reports

- `.remaining/` - Task tracking
  - Checklists for remaining work
  - Implementation requirements
